<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="how-adv">how <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /haʊ/    美 /haʊ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[指方式、方法] 怎样；怎么：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He knows how to write.
他知道该怎样写。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How shall I do it?
我应该怎么做呢？</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[指程度、数量、价值等] 多少；多么：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>How many</strong> days are there in a year?
一年有多少天？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>How much</strong> is the apple?
这苹果多少钱？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She wondered <strong>how much</strong> Angela already knew.
她想搞清楚安杰拉已经了解了多少。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>[口语] [指状态、情况] 怎样：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How is Jack?
杰克身体好吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How are things in your family?
你们家里的情况怎么样？</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>[表惊奇、高兴等] 多么；何等：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How high the kite is flying!
那风筝飞得多高啊！</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="how-can-could-sb-do-sth">How can / could sb do sth?</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[表示震惊或强烈反感] 某人怎么能做某事呢？</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How can you say such a thing?
你怎么能说这种话呢？</p></div>

<h3 id="how-come">How come (...)?</h3>
<p>1.<strong>怎么会 (…的)？</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How come David is always so full of energy?
大卫怎么会一直这么精力充沛？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— They didn't say a single word to each other today.
他们今天都没跟对方说一句话。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— How come?
怎么可能？</p></div>

<h3 id="how-far">how far</h3>
<p>1.<strong>多远：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How far did you go?
你走了多远？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How far away is the post office?
邮局离这里多远？</p></div>

<h3 id="how-long">how long</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[指时间段] 多长；多久：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How long have you been here?
你来这儿多长时间了？</p></div>

<h3 id="how-often">how often</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[指频率] 多长时间一次：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How often do you go there? Once or twice a week?
你多久去那儿一次？每周一次还是两次？</p></div>

<h3 id="how-soon">how soon</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[指将来] 多久：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How soon can you be ready?
你什么时候能准备好？</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>My mom told me how to preparing it.  （2020全国）  </li>
<li>By boat is the only way to get here, which is <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ we arrived.  （2018 江苏改）  </li>
<li>— Michael was late for Mr. Smith's chemistry class this morning.
— <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (怎么可能)? As far as I know, he never came late to class.  （2017 天津改）  </li>
<li>— Did you forget about my birthday?
— <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ I've booked a table at Michel's restaurant for this evening.  （2011 全国）<br />
A.What then?<br />
B.I'm afraid so.<br />
C.How could I?<br />
D.For sure.  </li>
<li>Students are always interested in finding out how <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ they can go with a new teacher.  （2008 安徽改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. preparing→prepare  2. how  3. How come  4. C  5. far  </p></div>